WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.734 --> 00:00:04.971 align:start size:78% position:22%
- Where's my van?
- Typical.

00:00:05.004 --> 00:00:07.874 align:start position:0%
Car stealing has
become more and more common

00:00:07.907 --> 00:00:12.578 align:start position:0%
especially in areas where people
are poor and need money for

00:00:12.611 --> 00:00:14.881 align:end size:53% position:53%
drugs or to feed
their children.

00:00:14.914 --> 00:00:18.785 align:end size:47% position:47%
But if her van
was outfitted

00:00:18.818 --> 00:00:22.355 align:start position:0%
with a Police Tek 2000
car alert system

00:00:22.388 --> 00:00:23.890 align:start position:0%
like my car is

00:00:23.923 --> 00:00:27.126 align:start position:0%
the scene would look
like this.

00:00:27.159 --> 00:00:30.096
Man, I sure could use this
car to sell it for drug money

00:00:30.129 --> 00:00:32.098
and some food for my baby.

00:00:32.131 --> 00:00:33.132
Here goes.

00:00:33.165 --> 00:00:35.301
[alarm wailing]

00:00:35.334 --> 00:00:38.271
[speaking in foreign language]

00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:50.683
Wow! You're right.
I should get a job.

00:00:50.716 --> 00:00:52.251
Stealing is for jerks.

00:00:52.284 --> 00:00:53.719
Thank God!

00:00:53.752 --> 00:00:56.589 align:start size:84% position:16%
Another car stealer off
the streets.

00:00:56.622 --> 00:00:59.826
Thanks to Police Tek.

00:00:59.859 --> 00:01:01.428
[alarm beeping]

